<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">فَصْلٌ:</span> يُكْرَهُ الْوِصَالُ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>, وَهُوَ أَنْ لَا يُفْطِرَ بَيْنَ الْيَوْمَيْنِ, لِأَنَّ النَّهْيَ رِفْقٌ وَرَحْمَةٌ,<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>